WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.900
I have already repaid the five-year kindness

2
00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:05.400
Do you remember what I said when I left?

3
00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:06.466
What did you say?

4
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:07.933
What did I say?

5
00:00:07.933 --> 00:00:09.300
I'll put it here.

6
00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:11.000
I will kneel and give Mengmeng to you.

7
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:12.766
If you dare to bully her in the future

8
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.833
I will definitely take her away standing up

9
00:00:14.866 --> 00:00:16.633
What did you say?

10
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:17.966
What did I say?

11
00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:21.666
You said what I said

12
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:25.700
You said you knelt down and gave Mengmeng to my mother

13
00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:27.800
If I dare not bully Mengmeng

14
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:30.433
You'll take her away standing up.

15
00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:33.266
Can I take Mengmeng away now?

16
00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:34.833
can

17
00:00:35.966 --> 00:00:36.866
Richest man

18
00:00:36.866 --> 00:00:38.266
Our whole family is sorry for you.

19
00:00:38.266 --> 00:00:39.366
It's all my fault

20
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.933
Our whole family has been punished

21
00:00:41.933 --> 00:00:43.666
You should take your breath away

22
00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:45.066
Let's go home

23
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:46.900
Let's take care of Mengmeng together, okay?

24
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:49.733
I will continue to be your wife and I will bring you tea and water

25
00:00:49.733 --> 00:00:51.000
I will do whatever is asked of me.

26
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.633
Can you give me another chance?

27
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:55.600
Chu Ruoxi, you know

28
00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:57.133
I just thought about it seriously

29
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:58.400
Five years.

30
00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:00.966
Have you ever, even just once?

31
00:01:00.966 --> 00:01:02.566
Be nice to me a little bit

32
00:01:02.566 --> 00:01:03.666
But it's a pity

33
00:01:03.666 --> 00:01:05.433
Not once.

34
00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:09.166
Lord Fu, what can I do to forgive me?

35
00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:11.100
Nothing to do.

36
00:01:11.300 --> 00:01:13.866
You and I are so far away

37
00:01:14.366 --> 00:01:15.800
It doesn't matter anymore

38
00:01:18.066 --> 00:01:20.800
God I really know I'm wrong

39
00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:22.566
Can you punish me?

40
00:01:22.566 --> 00:01:23.766
I'll do it myself

41
00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:26.366
It's my fault

42
00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:27.666
I'm cheap

43
00:01:28.700 --> 00:01:30.000
I opened my eyes

